0said%20in%20a%20Friday%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalnavy.mod.uk%2Fnews-and-latest-activity%2Fnews%2F2023%2Fnovember%2F17%2F20231117-royal-navys-successful-crewless-aircraft-trials-offer-glimpse-into-the-future%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMojave%20drones%20were%20developed%20from%20the%20MQ-1C%20Gray%20Eagle%20and%20MQ-9%20Reaper%20and%20are%20adapted%20for%20short%20take-offs%20and%20landings.%20They%20are%20nearly%2030%20feet%20long%20and%20have%20a%2056-foot-long%20wingspan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBritain%20said%20that%20no%20uncrewed%20system%20of%20this%20size%20%26quot%3Bhas%20ever%20flown%20from%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20outside%20the%20US%20Navy%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20trial%20also%20showed%20how%20drones%20can%20operate%20alongside%20crewed%20aircraft%20like%20the%20fifth-generation%20F-35%20stealth%20fighter%20jets%20stationed%20aboard%20the%20British%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20success%20of%20this%20trial%20heralds%20a%20new%20dawn%20in%20how%20we%20conduct%20maritime%20aviation%20and%20is%20another%20exciting%20step%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20Royal%20Navy's%20carrier%20strike%20group%20into%20a%20mixed%20crewed%20and%20uncrewed%20fighting%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20Rear%20Adm.%20James%20Parkin%2C%20who%20helped%20plan%20the%20trial%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20video%20shared%20by%20the%20official%20HMS%20Prince%20of%20Wales%20account%20to%20social%20media%20shows%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ga-asi.com%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Faircraft_systems%2Fpdf%2FMojave_Data_Sheet_120721.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMojave%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20capable%20of%20long-endurance%20missions%20and%20can%20be%20heavily%20armed%20with%20as%20many%20as%2016%20Hellfire%20missiles%2C%20operating%20from%20the%20deck%20of%20the%20carrier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embe