%3Bill-considered%20plan%20to%20feign%20the%20appearance%20of%20even-handedness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENYU%20Langone%20Health%20spokesman%20Steve%20Ritea%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20Friday%20in%20response%20to%20the%20suit%20that%20the%20medical%20facility%20%26quot%3Bstands%20by%26quot%3B%20its%20decision%20to%20terminate%20Neel%20and%20said%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Blooks%20forward%20to%20defending%20our%20decision%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20institution%20dedicated%20to%20healing%2C%20NYU%20Langone%20remains%20committed%20to%20providing%20a%20safe%20and%20inclusive%20environment%2C%20free%20of%20discrimination%2C%20for%20all%20of%20our%20employees%20and%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20Ritea%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20times%26quot%3B%20since%20last%20month%20the%20institution%20reminded%20all%20employees%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20standards%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20social%20media%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNonetheless%2C%20Dr.%20Ben%20Neel%2C%20as%20a%20leader%20at%20our%20institution%2C%20disregarded%20these%20standards%20in%20a%20series%20of%20public%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20later%20locked%20his%20Twitter%2FX%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20Ritea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeel's%20lawsuit%20says%20that%20the%20doctor%20was%20initially%20suspended%20over%20his%20posts%20and%20later%20fired%20on%20Nov.%2010%20in%20breach%20of%20his%20employee%20agreement%2C%20leaving%20his%20reputation%20in%20%26quot%3Btatters.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20is%20seeking%20a%20trial%20by%20jury%20and%20at%20least%20%24500%2C000%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDr.%20Neel%20was%20offered%20up%20as%20sacrificial%20lamb%20so%20that%20NYULH%20could%20feign%20impartiality%20in%20its%20effort%20to%20curb%20political%20and%20religious%20expression%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says%2C%20noting%20that%20another%20NYU%20physician%20was%20ousted%20over%20%26quot%3Bpro-Hamas%26quot%3B%2