0take%20the%20legal%20remedy%20and%20move%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20put%20a%20stay%20on%20this%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chautala%2C%20whose%20JJP%20(Jannayak%20Janta%20Party)%20is%20a%20junior%20partner%20in%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance%2C%20told%20NDTV%20in%20a%20telephonic%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20State%20Employment%20of%20Local%20Candidates%20Act%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20in%20November%202020%20and%20had%20received%20the%20governor's%20assent%20in%20March%202021%2C%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20brainchild%20of%20the%20Jannayak%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%2075%20per%20cent%20reservation%20in%20private%20sector%20jobs%20for%20state%20domiciled%20candidate%20was%20a%20key%20poll%20promise%20of%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20at%20the%20time%20of%202019%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20had%20stayed%20the%20Act%20in%20February%202022%20but%20the%20order%20had%20been%20set%20aside%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20days%20later%20following%20an%20appeal%20by%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20generate%20employment%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20It%20would%20have%20benefited%20the%20industry%20on%20two%20levels.%20First%2C%20they%20would%20not%20have%20had%20to%20pay%20transportation%20and%20accommodation%20cost%2C%20and%20second%2C%20local%20skilled%20labor%20would%20have%20been%20available.%20We%20have%20seen%20how%20industries%20are%20ruined%20when%20skilled%20workers%20go%20back%20to%20their%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chautala%2C%20underscoring%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chautala%20added%20that%20the%20industry%20was%20consulted%2C%20and%20their%20views%20were%20incorporated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnical%20jobs%20were%20dropped.%20The%20Act%20was%20for%20non-technica