975779-7461.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcoal-imports-case-sc-to-hear-in-feb-centre-s-appeal-against-bombay-hc-123111701295_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20court%20is%20likely%20to%20consider%20a%20fresh%20rejoinder%20filed%20by%20the%20DRI%20in%20the%20case%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcoal-imports-case-sc-to-hear-in-feb-centre-s-appeal-against-bombay-hc-123111701295_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcoal-imports-case-sc-to-hear-in-feb-centre-s-appeal-against-bombay-hc-123111701295_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcoal-imports-case-sc-to-hear-in-feb-centre-s-appeal-against-bombay-hc-123111701295_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Vows%2075%25%20Quota%20In%20Telangana%20Private%20Jobs%2C%20Court%20Junks%20Haryana%20Act%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20manifesto%20for%20the%20Telangana%20assembly%20polls%20released%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%2075%25%20reservation%20for%20residents%20of%20the%20state%20in%20private-sector%20jobs.%20Hours%20later%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20struck%20down%20a%20Haryana%20law%20implementing%20the%20same%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReservation%20based%20on%20domicile%20in%20private-sector%20jobs%20has%20always%20been%20a%20sticky%20subject%20and%20several%20industry%20associations%20have%20spoken%20against%20it%20in%20the%20past%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20is%20against%20the%20principles%20of%20justice%20and%20equality%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20Constitution.%20They%20have%20insisted%20that%20eligibility%20for%20such%20jobs%20should%20be%20based%20on%20merit%20and%20not%20where%20the%20person%20resides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20NDTV%20raised%20these%20issues%20with%20two%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Telangana%2C%20they%20said%20the%20idea%20is%20feasible%20and%20will%20be%20implemented%20after%20holding%20discussions%20with%20stakeholders.%20They%20emphasised%20that%20Telangana%20has%20a%20wealth%20of%20human%20capital%20and%20companies%20will%20not%20be%20deterred%20by%20the%20plan%20as%20long%20as%20they%20get%20skilled%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20and%20head%20of%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20committee%20D%20Sridhar%20Babu%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20definitely%20feasible.%20We%20will%20put%20it%20into%20action%20after%20we%20sit%20across%20and%20try%20to%20talk%20to%20various%20stakeholders%20who%20contribute%20to%20our%20economy.%20We%20will%20convince%20them%20and%20then%20implement%20our%20manifesto%20promise.%20Any%20industry%20requires%20a%20skilled%20force%20and%20that%20is%20what%20our%20youth%20in%20Telangana%20are.%20Industry%20will%20welcome%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20Mr%20Babu's%20comments%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Ajoy%20Kumar%20said%20it%20is%20important%20for%20local%20residents%20to%20get%20jobs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20lots%20of%20competent%20people%20in%20Telangana%2C%20let's%20first%20identify%20them.%20Our%20view%20is%20simple%2C%20entry-level%20jobs%2C%20engineers%2C%20Java%20programmers%2C%20anything%20else%2C%20why%20isn't%20it%20local%3F%20There%20are%20so%20many%20engineering%20colleges%2C%20so%20many%20talented%20people.%20If%20you%20do%20a%20quick%20dipstick%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu...%20they%20employ%20local%20people%20and%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20hubs%20of%20this%20country.%20So%2C%20all%20this%20is%20a%20myth.%20No%20capital%20gets%20scared%2C%20industries%20go%20where%20they%20can%20make%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20for%20Telangana's%20119%20Assembly%20seats%20will%20be%20held%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20November%2030%20and%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20December%203.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStriking%20down%20the%20Haryana%20State%20Employment%20of%20Local%20Candidates%20Act%2C%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%20termed%20it%20unconstitutional.%20The%20Act%2C%20which%20underwent%20several%20changes%20after%20it%20was%20passed%20in%202020%2C%20provided%20for%2075%25%20of%20private-sector%20jobs%20with%20a%20monthly%20salary%20or%20wages%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%2030%2C000%20being%20reserved%20for%20people%20with%20a%20resident%20or%20domicile%20certificate.%20The%20domicile%20requirement%20had%20also%20been%20brought%20down%20from%2015%20years%20to%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20sons-of-the-soil%20concept%20behind%20the%20law%20was%20an%20infringement%20of%20the%20constitutional%20rights%20of%20employers.%20They%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Act%20was%20against%20the%20principles%20of%20justice%2C%20equality%2C%20liberty%20and%20fraternity%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20concern%20was%20the%20impact%20the%20Act%20would%20have%20on%20the%20development%20of%20industry%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20Information%20Technology%20hubs%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700243460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fgis4n5u8_congress-telangana-manifesto_625x300_17_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-promises-75-quota-in-telangana-private-jobs-court-strikes-down-haryana-act-4583948%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20its%20manifesto%20for%20the%20Telangana%20assembly%20polls%20released%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%2075%25%20reservation%20for%20residents%20of%20the%20state%20in%20private-sector%20jobs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%