20a%20barrage%20of%20earthquakes%20that%20herald%20an%20impending%20volcanic%20eruption%2C%20some%20evacuated%20residents%20of%20the%20Icelandic%20town%20of%20Grindavik%20wonder%20if%20they%20will%20ever%20return.%20My%20mother%20said%20'I%20never%20want%20to%20go%20there%20again'%2C%26quot%3B%20Eythor%20Reynisson%2C%20who%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Grindavik%2C%20told%20AFP.%20The%20fishing%20port%20of%204%2C000%20people%20on%20Iceland's%20south%20coast%20was%20evacuated%20on%20November%2011%20after%20magma%20shifting%20under%20the%20Earth's%20crust%20caused%20hundreds%20of%20earthquakes%20--%20a%20warning%20of%20a%20likely%20volcanic%20eruption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fyears-of-uncertainty-ahead-for-iceland-volcano-town%2Farticleshow%2F105298709.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fyears-of-uncertainty-ahead-for-iceland-volcano-town%2Famp_articleshow%2F105298709.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fyears-of-uncertainty-ahead-for-iceland-volcano-town%2Famp_articleshow%2F105298709.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20And%20Bihar%20Now%20Top%20Blue-Collar%20Worker%20Suppliers%20To%20Gulf%20Nations%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%20have%20begun%20replacing%20Kerala%2C%20which%20was%20a%20significant%20contributor%20to%20the%20blue-collar%20workforce%2C%20from%20India%20to%20the%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20(GCC)%20region%2C%20a%20report%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20notable%20shift%20in%20migration%20patterns%2C%20with%20Kerala%20witnessing%20a%2090%20percent%20drop%20in%20workforce%20going%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20nations%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20blue-collar%20worker%20placement%20platform%20Huntr.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20void%20left%20by%20Kerala%20was%20filled%20by%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(UP)%20and%20Bihar%2C%20which%20are%20emerging%20as%20the%20top%20two%20contributors%20to%20the%20Gulf%20migration%20landscape%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20five%20labour-sending%20states%20include%20UP%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Kerala%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20while%20the%20preferred%20destinations%20remained%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20and%20Oman%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%2050%20percent%20increase%20in%20the%20migration%20of%20blue-collar%20workers%20from%20India%20to%20the%20GCC%20in%20the%20first%20seven%20months%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20by%20Huntr%20is%20based%20on%20data%20on%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20revealed%20that%20the%20demographic%20profile%20of%20Indian%20migrants%20to%20Dubai%20in%202023%20reveals%20a%20workforce%20primarily%20concentrated%20in%20the%2020-40%20age%20group%2C%20indicative%20of%20individuals%20in%20their%20prime%20working%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%20male-dominated%2C%20the%20workforce%20landscape%20is%20evolving%20with%20a%20notable%20increase%20in%20women%20migrants%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20hospitality%20sector%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQualifications%20among%20migrants%20vary%20widely%2C%20ranging%20from%20minimal%20formal%20education%20to%20vocational%20training%2C%20with%20skillsets%20tailored%20to%20specific%20job%20roles%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20these%20migrants%20hail%20from%20lower-income%20backgrounds%2C%20propelled%20by%20the%20aspiration%20for%20enhanced%20financial%20conditions%20through%20opportunities%20in%20Dubai's%20robust%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20employment%20landscape%20of%202024%20i