kdrop%20of%20rising%20inflation%20in%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20made%20a%20decision%20to%20lift%20from%20November%2017%20the%20temporary%20ban%20on%20exports%20of%20motor%20gasoline%20that%20it%20introduced%20on%20September%2021%20as%20part%20of%20a%20set%20of%20measures%20to%20stabilise%20the%20price%20situation%20on%20the%20domestic%20market%20of%20motor%20fuel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20energy%20ministry%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussia-says-lifting-temporary-ban-on-gasoline-exports-ministry%2Farticleshow%2F105298631.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussia-says-lifting-temporary-ban-on-gasoline-exports-ministry%2Famp_articleshow%2F105298631.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Frussia-says-lifting-temporary-ban-on-gasoline-exports-ministry%2Famp_articleshow%2F105298631.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rescue%20Work%20In%20Uttarakhand%20Tunnel%20Paused%20After%20Loud%20%26quot%3BCracking%20Sound%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20rescue%20ops%2C%20going%20on%20for%20six%20days%2C%20have%20hit%20another%20roadblock.%20The%20drilling%20operations%20have%20been%20put%20on%20hold%20after%202%3A45%20pm%2C%20said%20officials%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20meeting%20of%20experts%20has%20been%20called.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2040%20workers%20are%20trapped%20inside%20the%204.5-km%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20since%20Sunday%20morning%20when%20a%20part%20of%20the%20under-construction%20structure%20near%20Uttarkashi%20collapsed%20following%20a%20landslide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20execution%20of%20the%20work%20at%20around%202%3A45%20pm%2C%20a%20large%20scale%20cracking%20sound%20was%20heard%20by%20officials%20and%20the%20team%20working%20inside%20the%20tunnel%20and%20created%20a%20panic%20situation%20in%20the%20tunnel%20as%20well%20as%20to%20the%20team%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20National%20Highways%20%26amp%3B%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20(NHIDCL)%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20possibility%20that%20a%20further%20collapse%20may%20take%20place%20and%20accordingly%20pipe%20pushing%20activity%20has%20been%20stopped%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20situation%2C%20a%20meeting%20was%20called%20with%20all%20the%20officials%20and%20other%20experts%20of%20various%20organisations%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20efforts%20have%20been%20slowed%20by%20debris%20continuing%20to%20fall%20as%20workers%20laboured%20to%20clear%20the%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rescuers%20need%20to%20drill%20up%20to%2060%20metres%20to%20insert%20800%20mm%20and%20900%20mm%20diameter%20pipes%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20giant%20drill%20machine%20to%20create%20an%20escape%20passage%20for%20the%20stranded%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPositioning%20of%20the%20fifth%20pipe%20was%20under%20progress.%20It%20was%20reported%20that%20the%20machine%20was%20not%20able%20to%20push%20further%20as%20it%20was%20getting%20lifted%20and%20the%20bearings%20of%20the%20machine%20was%20damaged.%C2%A0%20It%20was%20planned%20to%20fix%20the%20machine%20by%20anchors%20to%20avoid%20uplifting.%20It%20was%20decided%20and%20agreed%20by%20the%20special%20agency%20executing%20the%20work%20that%20900%20mm%20diameter%20pipe%20that%20further%20pushing%20of%20the%20pipe%20will%20be%20feasible%20only%20if%20the%20machine%20is%20placed%20with%20the%20same%20inclination%20as%20the%20pipe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElite%20rescue%20teams%20from%20Thailand%20and%20Norway%2C%20including%20the%20one%20that%20successfully%20rescued%20the%20trapped%20children%20from%20a%20cave%20in%20Thailand%20in%