aland%20from%20a%20fresh%20to%20a%20used%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ICC%20later%20sent%20a%20clarification%20that%20there%20is%20no%20such%20rule%20of%20holding%20knock-out%20matches%20on%20a%20fresh%20track%20and%20Atkinson%20was%20apprised%20of%20the%20development%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20two%20senior%20BCCI's%20chief%20of%20ground%20staff%20Ashish%20Bhowmick%20and%20his%20second%20in%20command%20Taposh%20Chatterjee%2C%20along%20with%20former%20India%20seamer%20and%20BCCI's%20GM%20(Domestic%20Cricket)%20Abbey%20Kuruvilla%2C%20closely%20monitored%20the%20pitch%20preparations%20for%20the%20mega%20final%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20couldn't%20be%20confirmed%20if%20the%20track%20to%20be%20used%20for%20the%20final%20is%20a%20used%20one%20or%20a%20fresh%20surface.%20But%20the%20two%20senior%20curators%20and%20BCCI%20GM%20monitored%20the%20use%20of%20heavy%20roller%20on%20the%20designated%2022-yard%20strip.%20%26quot%3BIf%20heavy%20roller%20is%20being%20used%20on%20a%20black%20soil%20strip%20then%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20create%20a%20slow%20batting%20track%20where%20you%20can%20get%20a%20big%20score%20but%20you%20possibly%20can't%20consistently%20hit%20through%20the%20line.%20315%20could%20be%20a%20defendable%20score%20as%20batting%20second%20will%20be%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20state%20association%20curator%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20along%20with%20first%20team%20regulars%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20had%20an%20extensive%20net%20session%2C%20with%20reserve%20players%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20and%20Prasidh%20Krishna%20for%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20has%20been%20the%20custom%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Dravid%20spent%20a%20considerable%20amount%20of%20time%20looking%20at%20the%20track%20and%20also%20had%20extensive%20discussions%20with%20Bhowmick%20and%20Chatterjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700239020000%2C%22visual%22