0and%20Child%20Development%20as%20well%20as%20Minority%20Welfare%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20our%20workers%20fought%20against%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20in%20Amethi%20at%20a%20time%20when%20becoming%20a%20BJP%20or%20Sangh%20worker%20here%20was%20risky%2C%20painful%20and%20fatal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20our%20workers%20were%20not%20afraid%20of%20them%20and%20kept%20fighting.%20The%20workers%20struggled%20against%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%20Today%2C%20the%20result%20of%20that%20struggle%20is%20in%20front%20of%20you%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Brijesh%20Pathak%20and%20BJP%20State%20President%20Bhupendra%20Chaudhary.%20Blankets%20will%20be%20distributed%20among%208%2C000%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Irani%20said%20Amethi%20earlier%20saw%20only%20foundation%20stone-laying%20ceremonies%20but%20no%20inauguration%20ceremonies.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20only%20the%20stones%20of%20the%20industries%20were%20laid%20and%20there%20was%20no%20trace%20of%20that%20industry.%20Amethi%20was%20once%20known%20for%20closed%20industries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20government%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20many%20industries%20were%20established%20here%20and%20a%20large%20number%20of%20people%20were%20getting%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoans%20worth%20Rs%2022%2C000%20crores%20have%20been%20made%20available%20to%20people%20through%2011%20banks%20of%20Amethi%20district%20for%20setting%20up%20various%20industries%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Brijesh%20Pathak%20said%20the%20people%20who%20ruled%20Amethi%20for%20decades%20did%20not%20bring%20development%20here.%20People's%20representatives%20including%20pradhans%20were%20deprived%20of%20t