ilmed%20being%20whisked%20away%20on%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20golf%20cart%20loaded%20with%20operatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEntire%20families%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20families%20had%20seven%20members%20abducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETal%20Shoham%2C%2038%2C%20was%20taken%20from%20Beeri%2C%20the%20kibbutz%20community%20that%20saw%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20atrocities%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20together%20with%20six%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%20Adi%2C%2038%2C%20eight-year-old%20son%20Nave%20and%20three-year-old%20daughter%20Yahel%2C%20are%20also%20believed%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Gaza%2C%20as%20are%20Adi's%20mother%20Shoshan%20Haran%2C%2067%2C%20her%20aunt%2C%20Sharon%20Avigdori%2C%2052%2C%20and%20Sharon's%20daughter%20Noam%2C%20aged%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20members%20of%20their%20extended%20family%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20attacks%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20people%20were%20also%20taken%20from%20a%20family%20in%20Nir%20Oz%20kibbutz%2C%20which%20had%20at%20least%2073%20of%20its%20around%20400%20residents%20abducted%20--%20the%20highest%20number%20for%20a%20single%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharon%20Aloni%20Cunio%2C%2034%2C%20husband%20David%2C%2033%2C%20and%20their%20twin%20three-year-old%20daughters%20Emma%20and%20Yuly%2C%20were%20all%20seized%20on%20October%207.%20So%20were%20David's%20brother%20Ariel%20and%20Sharon's%20sister%20Danielle%20and%20Danielle's%20five-year-old%20daughter%20Amelia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanielle%2C%2044%2C%20appeared%20in%20a%20video%20released%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%2030%20along%20with%20two%20other%20women%20named%20in%20a%20statement%20by%20Netanyahu%20as%20Yelena%20Trupanov%20and%20Rimon%20Kirsht.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Aloni%20urged%20Netanyahu%20to%20agree%20a%20prisoner%20exchange%20with%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDozens%20more%20hostages%20were%20snatched%20from%20the%20Supernova%