eric%20oxygen%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20a%20permanent%20feature%20of%20habitable%20worlds%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20drop%20in%20oxygen%20is%20very%2C%20very%20extreme.%20We're%20talking%20around%20a%20million%20times%20less%20oxygen%20than%20there%20is%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Reinhard%2C%20from%20the%20Georgia%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20told%20New%20Scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20who%20predicted%20the%20doomsday%20scenario%20have%20said%20in%20the%20research%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20model%20projects%20that%20a%20deoxygenation%20of%20the%20atmosphere%2C%20with%20atmospheric%20O2%20dropping%20sharply%20to%20levels%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Archaean%20Earth%2C%20will%20most%20probably%20be%20triggered%20before%20the%20inception%20of%20moist%20greenhouse%20conditions%20in%20Earth's%20climate%20system%20and%20before%20the%20extensive%20loss%20of%20surface%20water%20from%20the%20atmosphere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20created%20detailed%20models%20of%20Earth's%20atmosphere%2C%20analysing%20changes%20in%20the%20brightness%20of%20the%20Sun%20and%20the%20corresponding%20drop%20in%20carbon%20dioxide%20levels.%20Less%20carbon%20dioxide%20means%20fewer%20photosynthesizing%20organisms%20such%20as%20plants%2C%20which%20would%20result%20in%20less%20oxygen.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700229000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fnaoo5i6_earth-generic_625x300_08_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhow-long-will-oxygen-rich-atmosphere-sustain-on-earth-study-says-4583202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shift%20will%20take%20Earth%20back%20to%20something%20like%20the%20state%20it%20was%20in%20before%20what's%20known%20as%20the%20Great%20Oxidation%20Event%20(GOE)%20around%202.4%20billion%20years%20ago%2C%20said%20the%20study.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhow-long-will-oxygen-rich-atmosphere-sustain-on-earth-study-says-4583202%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhow-long-will-oxygen-rich-atmosphere-sustain-on-earth-study-says-4583202%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fhow-long-will-oxygen-rich-atmosphere-sustain-on-earth-study-says-4583202%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Ma%20Would%20Come%20Home%20Covered%20in%20Coal%20Dust%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20Nancy%20Tyagi%20Won%20the%20Internet%20With%20Her%20Designing%20Talent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20came%20across%20Nancy%20Tyagi%E2%80%99s%20reel%20on%20Instagram%2C%20I%20found%20it%20quite%20unique.%20Not%20one%20to%20consume%20fashion%20content%2C%20what%20attracted%20me%20to%20Nancy%E2%80%99s%20was%20her%20sheer%20effort%20and%20talent.%20What%20separates%20this%2021-year-old%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20makes%20outfits%20from%20scratch%2C%20and%20takes%20you%2C%20the%20viewer%2C%20through%20the%20entire%20journey.%20She%20shows%20you%20the%20reality%20behind%20the%20glam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENancy%20is%20a%20self-taught%20seamstress%2C%20and%20her%20tryst%20with%20sewing%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F266909%2Fbarbie-dolls-desi-indian-mythological-stories-devaki-kerala-senior-citizen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethanks%20to%20her%20Barbies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20used%20to%20design%20outfits%20for%20her%20dolls.%20Little%20did%20she%20know%20then%20that%20this%20aptitude%20would%20be%20her%20breadwinner%20several%20years%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNancy-Tyagi-1-min-1700226962.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nan