m%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fhungarys-viktor-orban-seeks-to-stir-support-with-survey-questioning-eu-policies-ukraine-membership%2Famp_articleshow%2F105292381.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%E2%80%99s%20Alleged%20Irregularities%20on%20Import%20of%20Coal%20Again%20Under%20the%20Scanner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17154946%2Fimage-1516.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-seeks-restart-stalled-adani-coal-imports-probe-2023-11-17%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20cited%20court%20papers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20report%20that%20Adani%20Enterprises%20and%20its%20subsidiaries%20%E2%80%9Chave%20successfully%20mounted%20repeated%20legal%20challenges%20in%20India%20and%20Singapore%20to%20block%20the%20documents%E2%80%99%20release%E2%80%9D%2C%20referring%20to%20documents%20which%20would%20detail%20the%20true%20nature%20and%20value%20of%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20coal%20imports%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20been%20under%20the%20scanner%20and%20then%20again%20in%20sharp%20focus%20since%20the%20Hindenburg%20Research%20report%20in%20January%20referred%20to%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20coal%20imports.%20A%20detailed%20investigation%20by%20the%20London-based%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20alleged%20overvaluation%20of%20coal%20imports%E2%80%9D%20last%20month%2C%20connected%20alleged%20over-valuation%20of%20coal%20imports%20to%20inflated%20fuel%20prices%20and%20increased%20rates%20for%20electricity%20consumers%20may%20have%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20October%209%20legal%20filing%2C%20which%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20on%20Friday%20(November%2017)%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20has%20%E2%80%9Casked%20India%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20quash%20a%20previous%20lower%20court%20order%20that%20allowed%20Adani%20to%20block%20authorities%20from%20collecting%20evidence%20from%20Singapore.%E2%80%9D%20DRI%20says%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20company%20%5Bhas%5D%20thwarted%20%5Bthe%20move%20to%20share%20documents%20with%20authorities%5D%20for%20years%2C%20as%20per%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20has%20denied%20wrongdoing%2C%20and%20told%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cfully%20cooperated%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20authorities%20by%20providing%20details%20and%20documents%20sought%20more%20than%20four%20years%20ago%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20deficiency%20or%20objection%E2%80%9D%20was%20communicated%20by%20investigators%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20that%20ahead%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%202024%20election%2C%20political%20opponents%20have%20increased%20pressure%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20administration%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20favouritism%20toward%20Adani%20in%20government%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20and%20Adani%2C%20who%20both%20hail%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20have%20denied%20impropriety%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fmodi-adani-oligarchy-stock-offshore%5C%22%3EThe%20Undeniable%20Rise%20of%20Oligarchic%20Capitalism%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOver-invoicing%20Imports%20%3D%20Consumers%20Overpaying%20for%20Electricity%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-coal-imports-over-pricing-customers-overcharged-fuel-ft%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520detailed%2520FT%2520investigation%2520points%2Chidden%2520shareholder%2520in%2520Adani%2520firms.%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%2C%20according%20to%20data%20obtained%20from%20customs%20records%2C%20that%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20%E2%80%9Cappears%20to%20have%20imported%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20coal%20at%20prices%20well%20above%20market%20value.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdata%20supports%20longstanding%20allegations%20that%20Adani%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20private%20coal%20importer%2C%20has%20been%20inflating%20fuel%20costs%20and%20led%20millions%20of%20Indian%20consumers%20and%20businesses%20to%20overpay%20for%20electricity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20London-based%20broadsheet%20examined%20data%20between%202019%20and%202021%2C%20and%20concluded%20that%20%E2%80%9CAdani%20used%20offshore%20intermediaries%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20Dubai%20and%20Singapore%20to%20import%20%245%20billion-worth%20of%20coal%20at%20prices%20that%20were%20at%20times%20more%20than%20double%20the%20market%20price.%E2%80%9D%20It%20cited%20journeys%20of%20coal%2C%20during%20which%20the%20price%20of%20coal%2C%20%E2%80%9Cunaccountably%20increased%20by%20over%20%2470%20million.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20again%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20coal%20imports%20over-pricing%20allegations%20which%20had%20been%20dogging%20the%20Adanis%20despite%20denials.%20The%20Opposition%20Congress%20party%20alleged%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fadani-group-likely-overbilled-coal-consumers-by-12000-crore-congress%2Farticle67417527.ece%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cmay%20be%20behind%20the%20biggest%20scam%20modern%20India%20has%20seen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20They%20cited%20the%20fresh%20revelations%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20to%20indicate%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20than%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore%20may%20have%20been%20siphoned%20out%20of%20the%20country%20in%20two%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20general%20secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20claimed%20that%20this%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20a%20metaphorical%20loot%20but%20literally%20theft%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20pockets%20of%20crores%20of%20Indians.%20He%20said%20the%20latest%20revelations%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20examined%2030%20Adani%20coal%20shipments%20between%202019%20and%202021%20amounting%20to%203.1%20million%20tonnes%2C%20found%20a%2052%25%20profit%20even%20on%20a%20low%20margin%20business%20like%20coal%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGujarat%20Police%20%E2%80%98summons%E2%80%99%20journalists%20reporting%20on%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20coal%20irregularities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20consistently%20denied%20charges%20that%20there%20is%20any%20personal%20friendship%20or%20connection%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20that%20have%20allowed%20Adani%20to%20grow%20at%20the%20fastest%20pace%20any%20conglomerate%20has%20in%20recent%20times%20and%20managed%20to%20control%20large%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20India.%20But%20Gujarat%20police%E2%80%99s%20enthusiasm%20in%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%98summon%E2%80%99%20journalists%20who%20are%20reporting%20on%20allegations%20of%20impropriety%20in%20how%20the%20Adani%20Group%20functions%20have%20only%20added%20grist%20to%20the%20mill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20on%20Friday%20(November%2010)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-grants-financial-times-journalists-interim-protection-from-gujarat-police-arrest-over-article-against-adani-group-242062%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Supreme%2520Court%2520on%2520Friday%2CAugust%2520against%2520the%2520Adani%2520group.%5C%22%3Eto%20grant%20%E2%80%9Cinterim%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20coercive%20action%20to%20two%20journalists%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Benjamin%20Nicholas%20Brooke%20Parkin%20and%20Chloe%20Nina%20Cornish%2C%20who%20have%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20Police%20in%20relation%20to%20an%20article%20published%20in%20August%20against%20the%20Adani%20group.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Farticle-on-adani-group-supreme-court-grants-protection-to-2-journalists-summoned-by-gujarat-police%2Farticle67522547.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20to%20grant%20interim%20protection%20to%20two%20other%20journalists%20Ravi%20Nair%20and%20Anand%20Mangnale%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20investigation%20by%20them%20on%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20of%20an%20Opposition%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20has%20already%20drawn%20attention%20to%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fethics-committee-summons-mahua-moitra-on-oct-31-ignoring-mps-requests-to-delay-until-festival%5C%22%3EParliamentary%20procedures%2C%20rules%20and%20propriety%20may%20have%20been%20stretched%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20often%20violated%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20looking%20into%20the%20matter%20of%20how%20she%20asked%20questions%20in%20Parliament.%20Moitra%20and%20her%20colleagues%20across%20Opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20Committee%20say%20she%20is%20being%20targeted%20as%20she%20raises%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20infrastructure%20conglomerate%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House%20which%20becomes%20hard%20to%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20120%20eminent%20citizens%20have%20also%20linked%20the%20contentious%20recommendation%20of%20expulsion%20of%20Mahua%20Moitra%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1059163%2Fexpelling-mahua-moitra-would-be-against-public-interest-say-over-120-eminent-citizens%5C%22%3Eas%20being%20%E2%80%9Cagainst%20public%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20They%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20allegations%20agai