0declining%20poverty%20are%20pivoted%20on%20thin%20ice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20near%20term%2C%202QFY24%20results%20exemplify%20the%20household%20budget%20constraints%20imparting%20muted%20demand%20conditions%20for%20the%20whole%20gamut%20of%20consumer%20companies%20ranging%20from%20consumer%20staples%2C%20consumer%20discretionary%2C%20apparel%2C%20undergarments%2C%20organized%20retail%2C%20and%20consumer%20electricals%2C%20which%20comprise%20the%20fat%20lower%20arm%20of%20the%20K-shape.%20The%20upper%20arm%20is%20represented%20by%20relatively%20better%20the%20Auto%20sector%20and%20luxury%20consumption%2C%20which%20are%20also%20fuelled%20by%20leverage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EExhibit%202%3A%20Real%20income%20of%20long%20shift%20food%20delivery%20workers%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17115745%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-11.57.39%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17115745%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-11.57.39%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17115745%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-11.57.39%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x61.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17115745%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-11.57.39%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x208.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22244%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20NCAER%20Food%20delivery%20Platform%20Workers%20(2022)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDhananjay%20Sinha%20is%20co-head%20of%20Equities%20and%20he