ESanchez%3A%20%E2%80%98A%20united%20Spain%20is%20a%20better%20Spain%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchez%20defended%20the%20amnesty%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20two-day%20parliamentary%20debate%2C%20arguing%20it%20was%20needed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cheal%20the%20wounds%E2%80%9D%20opened%20by%20the%20wealthy%20northeastern%20region%E2%80%99s%20independence%20push.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20guarantee%20the%20unity%20of%20Spain%20through%20dialogue%20and%20forgiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2051-year-old%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Catalonia%20and%20other%20regions%20there%20are%20citizens%20who%20believe%20that%20they%20would%20be%20better%20going%20their%20own%20way.%20This%20government%20believes%20that%20a%20united%20Spain%20is%20a%20better%20Spain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerman%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20world%20leaders%20to%20congratulate%20Sanchez%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20good%20that%20we%20can%20continue%20to%20work%20side%20by%20side.%20We%20see%20many%20challenges%20in%20the%20world%20from%20a%20very%20similar%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanchez%20accused%20of%20%E2%80%98political%20corruption%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20critics%20have%20accused%20Sanchez%20of%20trampling%20on%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20selling%20out%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdopting%20measures%20that%20go%20against%20the%20general%20interest%20in%20exchange%20of%20personal%20benefit%20is%20political%20corruption%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20conservative%20Popular%20Party%20(PP)%2C%20Alberto%20Nunez%20Feijoo%2C%20said%20during%20the%20debate%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeijoo%20won%20the%20most%20seats%20in%20the%20election%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20secure%20enough%20support%20from%20other%20parties%20in%20his%20own%20bid%20to%20for%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20the%20far-right%20Vox%20party%2C%20Santiago%20Abascal%2C%20went%20even%20further%2C%20calling%20the%20amnesty%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccoup%20d%E2%80%99etat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20vote%2C%20Feijoo%20walked%20across%20the%20chamber%20to%20shake%20Sanchez%E2%80%99s%20hand%20as%20leftist%20lawmakers%20applauded%20and%20cheered%2C%20while%20Vox%20party%20leader%20Abascal%20walked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%20of%20the%20house%20will%20now%20convey%20the%20result%20to%20King%20Felipe%20VI.%20Once%20published%20in%20the%20State%20Gazette%2C%20Sanchez%20will%20be%20sworn%20as%20the%20new%20prime%20minister%20before%20the%20king%2C%20most%20likely%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpain%20protests%20threaten%20to%20turn%20violent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20polls%20show%20over%20half%20of%20all%20Spaniards%20oppose%20the%20amnesty%20and%2C%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20have%20joined%20street%20demonstrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20protests%20backed%20by%20right-wing%20political%20parties%20turned%20violent%20when%20riot%20police%20used%20batons%20and%20shields%20to%20beat%20back%20crowds%20gathered%20outside%20the%20Socialist%20party%20headquarters%20in%20Madrid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%201%2C600%20police%20were%20deployed%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday%20for%20the%20parliamentary%20debate%20and%20vote%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Interior%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20Sanchez%E2%80%99s%20other%20policies%20are%20economic%20plans%20including%20making%20public%20transport%20free%20for%20young%20people%20and%20the%20unemployed%2C%20and%20continuing%20to%20link%20pension%20hikes%20to%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20coalition%2C%20which%20includes%20smaller%2C%20leftist%2C%20regional%20parties%20with%20different%20ideologies%2C%20could%20make