3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20picture%20is%20that%20after%20audaciously%20claiming%20the%20mantle%20of%20leadership%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20as%20recently%20as%20in%20September%2C%20in%20a%20span%20of%20over%20two%20months%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0is%20gliding%20over%20to%20the%20American%20camp%20as%20the%20US%E2%80%99%20indispensable%20ally%2C%20even%20aspiring%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cglobal%20defence%20hub%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20takeaways%20of%20the%202%2B2%20meeting%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESharing%20technology%20relating%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmaritime%20challenges%2C%20including%20in%20the%20undersea%20domain%E2%80%9D%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECo-development%20and%20co-production%20of%20ground%20mobility%20systems%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0to%20undertake%20US%20aircraft%20maintenance%20and%20mid-voyage%20repair%20of%20US%20naval%20vessels%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUS%20investment%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20maintenance%2C%20repair%20and%20overhaul%20of%20US%20aircraft%20and%20UAVs%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFinalisation%20of%20a%20Security%20of%20Supply%20Arrangement%2C%20which%20would%20deepen%20the%20integration%20of%20defence%20industrial%20ecosystems%20and%20strengthen%20supply%20chain%20resilience%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECreation%20of%20new%20liaison%20positions%20between%20the%20two%20armed%20forces%20further%20to%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20full%20membership%20of%20the%20multinational%20Combined%20Maritime%20Forces%2C%20headquartered%20in%20Bahrain%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaximisation%20of%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20Logistics%20and%20Exchange%20Memorandum%20Agreement%2C%20and%20identify%20steps%20to%20enhance%20the%20reach%20of%20the%20US%20naval%20vessels%20to%20Indian%20bases.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%2C%20the%20above%20is%20only%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%2C%20while%20this%20extraordinary%20transition%20in%20Indian%20policies%20will%20largely%20remain%20behind%20closed-doors.%20The%20US%20seems%20supremely%20confident%20that%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0is%20ready%20to%20enter%20into%20an%20exclusive%20alliance%2C%20something%20that%20New%20Delhi%20never%20sought%20with%20any%20big%20power.%20What%20is%20the%20offer%20that%20the%20Biden%20Administration%20has%20made%20to%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20latter%20cannot%20refuse%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fat-2-plus-2-meet-us-asks-india-to-join-canada-probe-both-sides-support-israel%5C%22%3EUS%20Asks%20India%20to%20Join%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20Probe%2C%20Both%20Jointly%20Express%20Support%20For%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20such%20a%20massive%20shift%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20military%20policies%20needs%20to%20be%20correlated%20with%20the%20fundamental%20postulates%20of%20foreign%20policy.%20But%20call%20it%20%E2%80%9Cbipartisan%20consensus%E2%80%9D%20or%20whatever%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20main%20Opposition%20party%20apparently%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care.%20This%20is%20not%20surprising.%20The%20shift%20is%20actually%20about%20a%20nascent%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E-US%20alliance%20to%20counter%20China%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20is%20a%20policy%20front%20where%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20choose%20between%20Tweedledum%20and%20Tweedledee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20China%20understand%20that%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20is%20transitioning%2C%20but%20they%20pretend%20not%20to%20notice.%20At%20any%20rate%2C%20their%20capacity%20to%20leverage%20Indian%20policies%20has%20dramatically%20shrunk%20%E2%80%94%20Moscow%E2%80%99s%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0is%20not%20ecstatic%20about%20growing%20multipolarity.%20It%20is%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Crules-based%20order%E2%80%9D%20and%20feels%20far%20more%20comfortable%20with%20a%20bipolar%20world%20in%20which%20the%20US%20is%20pre-eminent%2C%20developing%20its%20national%20power%20with%20China%E2%80%99s%20hegemonic%20instincts%20in%20check.%20Today%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20align%20with%20the%20US%20is%20more%20evident%20than%20ever%20before.%20The%20animus%20against%20China%E2%80%99s%20rise%20was%20palpable%20at%20the%202%2B2%20meeting.%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0has%20cast%20away%20any%20residual%20pretensions%20and%20is%20shifting%20toward%20an%20openly%20adversarial%20relationship%20with%20China.%20The%20Quad%20has%20become%20an%20important%20locomotive.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20a%20Chinese%20response%20can%20be%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20possible%20because%20Delhi%20feels%20reasonably%20assured%20that%20Washington%E2%80%99s%20Indo-Pacific%20focus%20remains%20intact%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20despite%20growing%20engagement%20with%20China%20%E2%80%95%20Xi%20Jinping%E2%80%99s%20first%20trip%20to%20the%20US%20in%20five%20years%2C%20and%20a%20summit%20meeting%20with%20President%20Biden%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fd4eb7bd0-65ba-4a1b-8b20-049ced9355d0%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fd4eb7bd0-65ba-4a1b-8b20-049ced9355d0%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1700274461637000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3A5Lk3lB_HU7dMPdYpF0A3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20the%20Sino-American%20relationship%20more%20predictable%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20regional%20issues%20that%20figured%20prominently%20at%20the%202%2B2%20were%20Afghanistan%2C%20Ukraine%20and%