er%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fb7cdd688-ad5f-4ede-b21c-4318b901c208%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fb7cdd688-ad5f-4ede-b21c-4318b901c208%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1700274461637000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2yLHXGgKOpIQ25UU4nLfyL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0road%20connecting%20Afghanistan%20via%20Wakhan%20Corridor%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20game-changer%20in%20geo-strategy.%20The%20security%20of%20Xinjiang%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20incessant%20interest%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202%2B2%20joint%20statement%20signals%20a%20renewed%20US-Indian%20convergence%20on%20Afghanistan.%20How%20far%20this%20would%20translate%20into%20proactive%20moves%20is%20a%20moot%20point.%20Notably%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20are%20also%20exploiting%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20preoccupations%20with%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20double%20down%20on%20their%20post-Cold%20War%20strategy%20to%20roll%20back%20Russian%20influence%20in%20Afghanistan.%20Moscow%20senses%20that%20it%20is%20losing%20ground%20in%20its%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20conflict%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Indian%20sides%20have%20harmonised%20their%20positions.%20Delhi%20is%20shedding%20its%20strategic%20ambivalence%20and%20moving%20towards%20the%20US%20position.%20This%20comes%20out%20in%20what%20the%20joint%20statement%20says%2C%20and%20what%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20On%20Ukraine%2C%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20attritional%20war%20has%20%E2%80%9Cconsequences%20predominantly%20affecting%20the%20global%20South.%E2%80%9D%20This%20apart%2C%20Moscow%20can%20learn%20to%20live%20with%20the%202%2B2%20formulation%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20regards%20the%20West%20Asian%20situation%2C%20the%20joint%20statement%20voices%20vehement%20support%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20fight%20against%20%E2%80%9Cterrorism%E2%80%9D.%20Here%2C%20again%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0refuses%20to%20call%20out%20Hamas.%20Nor%20is%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0endorsing%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Hamas%2C%20leave%20alone%20pre-judge%20its%20chances%20of%20success.%20Most%20important%2C%20the%20joint%20statement%20omits%20any%20reference%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20self-defence%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20mantra%20that%20is%20constantly%20on%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20lips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%20cannot%20possibly%20call%20the%20Gaza%20war%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cself%20defence%E2%80%9D%20when%20Israel%20has%20unleashed%20such%20a%20brutal%20military%20operation%20against%20hapless%20civilians%20and%20razed%20Gaza%20City%20to%20the%20ground.%20It%E2%80%99s%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20joint%20British-American%20aerial%20bombing%20attack%20on%20Dresden%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20which%20killed%20over%2025%2C000%20German%20people%20on%20the%20night%20of%20March%209-10%2C%201945.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20all%20these%20diplomatic%20peregrinations%20through%20the%20Valley%20of%20Death%20could%20be%20better%20understood%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20intense%20back-channel%20dealings%20involving%20the%20Hamas%20leadership%20in%20regional%20capitals%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Biden%20administration%20would%20have%20high%20stakes%20and%20is%20a%20participant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.K.%20Bhadrakumar%20is%20a%20retired%20diplomat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%2C%20excerpted%20from%20Indianpunchline.com%C2%A0was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700198255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17103838%2FF-kDD_eXcAAwo98-e1700197751446.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-two-months-india-transitioned-from-aspiring-global-south-leader-to-plain-us-ally%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202%2B2%20joint%20statement%20signals%20a%20renewed%20US-Indian%20convergence%20on%20Afghanistan.%20How%20far%20this%20would%20translate%20into%20proactive%20moves%20is%20a%20moot%20point.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-two-months-india-transitioned-from-aspiring-global-south-leader-to-plain-us-ally%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Government%20Minister%20Writes%20to%20ED%20and%20CBI%20Directors%20to%20Investigate%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17100626%2FF-lTnQZW8AA_eoE.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Delhi%20vigilance%20minister%20Atishi%20yesterday%20(Thursday%2C%20November%2017)%20has%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20possible%20conflict%20of%20interest%20arising%20in%20a%20matter%20related%20to%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20land%20acquisition%20case%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20secretary%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20in%20letters%20she%20has%20written%20to%20the%20directors%20of%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecommending%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20south%20west%20Delhi%20district%20magistrate%2C%20Hemant%20Kumar%2C%20and%20division%20commissioner%2C%20Ashwani%20Kumar%2C%20in%20the%20Dwarka%20E-way%20land%20compensation%20award%20case%2C%20Atishi%20said%20has%20said%20this%20was%20a%20fit%20case%20for%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20chief%20secretary%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-chief-secretary-nhai-land-compensation%5C%22%3Edenied%3C%2Fa%3E%20any%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20land%20acquisition%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20had%20forwarded%20a%20670%20page%20report%20prepared%20by%20the%20vigilance%20department%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20flagging%20%E2%80%9Cabuse%20of%20authority%20by%20the%20high-ranking%20officials%E2%80%9D%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20(LG)%20Vinay%20Saxena.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20the%20investigative%20agencies%20to%20take%20cognizance%20of%20the%20vigilance%20report%20which%20is%20why%20the%20minister%20has%20forwarded%20it%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20agencies%20would%20act%20on%20source%20information%20and%20register%20a%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Delhi%20government%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20CBI%20flags%20this%20as%20a%20suitable%20case%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%2C%C2%A0%201988%2C%20the%20letter%20to%C2%A0%20the%20ED%20points%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9C93%25%20of%20payment%20of%20the%20land%20purchased%20by%20the%20beneficiaries%20may%20have%20been%20done%20in%20cash%E2%80%A6which%20might%20involve%20money%20laundering%20as%20well%20making%20it%20a%20case%20fit%20for%20investigation%20by%20the%20ED%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20to%20the%20agencies%20said%20that%20as%20per%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20vigilance%20department%2C%20%E2%80%9Csince%20the%20land%20was%20purchased%20by%20the%20beneficiaries%20at%20only%207%25%20of%20the%20circle%20rate%20in%202015%2C%20there%20is%20a%20likelihood%20that%20the%20remaining%2093%25%20payment%20may%20have%20been%20done%20in%20cash.%20It%20appears%20that%20the%20exorbitant%20award%20of%20land%20compensation%20is%20not%20only%20a%20case%20of%20corruption%20but%20might%20involve%20money%20laundering%20as%20well%20making%20it%20a%20case%20fit%20for%20investigation%20by%20the%20ED%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vigilance%20minister%20writes%20in%20her%20letter%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20directed%20me%20to%20send%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20aforesaid%20preliminary%20report%20to%20you%20with%20a%20request%20that%20the%20case%20be%20registered%20by%20ED%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%202002%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20alleged%20illegal%20transactions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20goes%20onto%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20examined%20the%20allegations%20based%20on%20the%20certified%20copies%20of%20the%20relevant%20files%20provided%20by%20the%20Special%20Secretary%20(Vigilance).%20No%20files%20whatsoever%20have%20been%20received%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20(Revenue)-cum-Divisional%20Commissioner%20despite%20asking%20for%20the%20same.%20Besides%2C%20I%20have%20also%20referred%20to%20publicly%20available%20documents%20related%20to%20land%20records%2C%20reports%2C%20and%20records%20available%20on%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%20I%20submitted%20the%20preliminary%20report%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi%20on%2014.11.2023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20of%20the%20vigilance%20minister%20further%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20also%20forwarded%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20preliminary%20report%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20for%20registering%20a%20case%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%201988%20and%20such%20other%20provisions%20of%20law%20as%20may%20be%20applicable%20in%20this%20case%20against%20Naresh%20Kumar%20(Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Delhi)%2C%20and%20Ashwini%20Kumar%20(Divisional%20Commissioner%2C%20Delhi)%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20DM%20South%20West%20Hemant%20Kumar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20letter%20to%20CBI%20director%2C%20Atishi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20understand%20that%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Delhi%20has%20already%20referred%20certain%20aspects%20related%20to%20this%20case%20to%20CBI%3B%20particularly%2C%20the%20action%20of%20the%20then%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20South%20West%20Delhi%20in%20enhancing%20the%20land%20compensation%20exorbitantly.%20However%2C%20as%20you%20will%20find%20in%20this%20preliminary%20report%2C%20the%20then%20DM%20may%20just%20have%20executed%20the%20unlawful%20directions%20of%20his%20superiors.%20Therefore%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20then%20DM%2C%20the%20role%20of%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20Ashwani%20Kumar%2C%20Principal%20Revenue%20Secretary-cum-Divisional%20Commissioner)%20too%20should%20be%20investigated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vigilance%20report%20says%20the%20enhanced%20compensation%20amounted%20to%20Rs%20850%20Cr%20and%20not%20Rs%20353%20crore%20as%20was%20initially%20presumed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20vigilance%20report%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20enhanced%20compensation%20for%20the%20claimants%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20award%20order%20passed%20by%20DM%20is%20Rs.%20856%20crore%20rupees%20and%20not%20Rs.%20311%20crore%20as%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20inquiry%20report%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20(DOV).%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Divisional%20Commissioner%20accepted%20this%20report%2C%20and%20did%20not%20raise%20any%20objections%20to%20the%20flawed%20approach%20adopted%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20(DOV)%20in%20its%20calculations%20thereby%20undercounting%C2%A0%20the%20extent%20of%20loss%20to%20the%20government%20exchequer.%20Further%2C%20the%20role%20of%20Shri%20Hemant%20Kumar%20is%20suspect%20and%20vigilance%20inquiry%2C%20prima-facie%2C%20raises%20serious%20questions%20on%20his%20financial%20propriety.%20A%20thorough%20investigation%20by%20the%20CBI%20will%20reveal%20the%20complete%20truth.%20However%2C%20this%20Rs%20856%20crore%20enhanced%20compensation%20is%20only%20a%20part%20of%20the%20story%20and%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20windfall%20gains%20can%20be%20calculated%20only%20after%20examination%20of%20how%20much%20they%20paid%20to%20purchase%20the%20land%20in%20question.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20secretary%20has%20denied%20any%20wrong%20doing.%20He%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20week%2C%20%E2%80%9CCVO-cum-Chief%20Secretary%20took%20proactive%20action%20against%20the%20delinquent%20officer%20Sh.%20Hemant%20Kumar%20(IAS%2C%20AGMUT%202013)%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20he%20was%20firstly%20transferred%20out%20from%20Delhi%20to%20ANI%20(Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands)%20on%2019.10.2023%20and%20then%20was%20placed%20under%20suspension%20on%2020.10.2023.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20is%20also%20contesting%20any%20proposed%20extension%20in%20service%20of%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20secretary%20by%20the%20union%20government%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%20The%20chief%20secretary%20superannuates%20November%2030.%20The%20next%20date%20of%20hearing%20is%20November%2020.%20Notices%20have%20already%20been%20issued%20to%20the%20parties%20concerned%2C%20including%20the%20union%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700195955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17100626%2FF-lTnQZW8AA_eoE.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-atishi-ed-cbi-chief-secretary-naresh-kumar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20comes%20shortly%20after%20CM%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20forwarded%20a%20vigilance%20report%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Delhi%20that%20takes%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20land%20overvaluation%20case%20where%20the%20chief%20secretary%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20having%20a%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-atishi-ed-cbi-chief-secretary-naresh-kumar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'US%20Credibility%20at%20Stake'%3A%20The%20Elders%20Write%20to%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20Israel-Hamas%20Conflict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17093901%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-9.38.00.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Elders%20is%20an%20international%20non-governmental%20organisation%20of%20public%20figures%20noted%20as%20senior%20statesmen%2C%20peace%20activists%20and%20human%20rights%20advocates%2C%20who%20were%20brought%20together%20by%20Nelson%20Mandela%20in%202007.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThey%20include%20key%20past%20and%20present%20world%20leaders%2C%20including%20former%20heads%20of%20states%20and%20governments.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOn%20November%2016%2C%202023%2C%20The%20Elders%20delivered%20an%20open%20letter%20to%20US%20president%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20letter%20has%20as%20its%20signatories%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMary%20Robinson%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Ireland%20and%20Chair%20of%20The%20Elders%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBan%20Ki-moon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20UN%20Secretary-General%20and%20Deputy%20Chair%20of%20The%20Elders%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGra%C3%A7a%20Machel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Founder%20of%20the%20Gra%C3%A7a%20Machel%20Trust%2C%20co-founder%20and%20Deputy%20Chair%20of%20The%20Elders%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGro%20Harlem%20Brundtland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Norway%20and%20former%20Director-General%20of%20the%20WHO%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelen%20Clark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20New%20Zealand%20and%20former%20UN%20Development%20Programme%20Administrator%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElbegdorj%20Tsakhia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eformer%20President%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Mongolia%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EZeid%20Ra%E2%80%99ad%20Al%20Hussein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHina%20Jilani%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Advocate%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20co-chair%20of%20the%20Taskforce%20on%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEllen%20Johnson%20Sirleaf%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Liberia%20and%20Nobel%20Peace%20Laureate%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERicardo%20Lagos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Chile%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJuan%20Manuel%20Santos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Colombia%20and%20Nobel%20Peace%20Laureate%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EErnesto%20Zedillo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20former%20President%20of%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20the%20letter%20is%20below.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDear%20President%20Biden%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20a%20historic%20opportunity%20to%20help%20end%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20polarisation%20increases%2C%20the%20world%20needs%20you%20to%20set%20out%20a%20vision%20for%20peace.%20That%20vision%20must%20give%20hope%20to%20those%20who%20reject%20extremism%20and%20want%20the%20violence%20to%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20urge%20you%20to%20do%20two%20things%3A%20set%20out%20a%20serious%20peace%20plan%2C%20and%20help%20build%20a%20new%20coalition%20for%20peace%20to%20deliver%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20understand%20you%20want%20to%20help%20make%20Israelis%20safe.%20We%20share%20that%20objective%2C%20and%20have%20condemned%20the%20horrific%20Hamas%20attacks%20of%207%20October.%20We%20share%20too%20your%20commitment%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20self-determination.%20Palestinian%20and%20Israeli%20lives%20are%20of%20equal%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDestroying%20Gaza%20and%20killing%20civilians%20are%20not%20making%20Israelis%20safe.%20These%20actions%20will%20breed%20more%20terrorism%2C%20across%20the%20region%20and%20beyond.%20There%20is%20no%20military%20solution%20to%20this%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20is%20already%20feeding%20antisemitism%20and%20islamophobia%2C%20including%20in%20the%20USA.%20It%20undermines%20your%20other%20objectives%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20credibility%20and%20interests%20across%20the%20world%20are%20at%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20policies%20of%20expanding%20illegal%20settlements%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20normalising%20relations%20with%20Arab%20countries%20while%20bypassing%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20have%20not%20made%20Israelis%20safe.%20Successive%20US%20governments%20have%20been%20complicit%20in%20these%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20way%20to%20make%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinians%20safe%20is%20a%20lasting%20political%20solution.%20It%20must%20guarantee%20the%20security%20of%20Israel%2C%20whose%20people%20remain%20under%20threat.%20And%20it%20must%20meet%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20legitimate%20aspirations%20for%20their%20own%20state.%20Long%20denied%20during%2056%20years%20of%20occupation%2C%20these%20hopes%20are%20fading%20fast%2C%20as%20innocent%20Palestinians%20die%20in%20the%20rubble%20of%20Gaza%20and%20the%20stolen%20lands%20of%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20too%20long%20the%20world%20has%20spoken%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution%20while%20allowing%20Israel%20to%20build%20a%20one-state%20reality.%20This%20has%20suited%20extremists%20in%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20who%20deny%20the%20other%20country%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20exist.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20end%20the%20empty%20rhetoric%2C%20and%20implement%20a%20serious%20peace%20plan%20that%20undermines%20extremists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20plan%20should%20answer%20who%20runs%20Gaza%20next%2C%20end%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20accelerating%20annexation%20of%20Palestinian%20land%2C%20and%20address%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20legitimate%20security%20concerns.%20It%20must%20recognise%20the%20equal%20rights%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20Israelis%2C%20and%20be%20rooted%20in%20international%20law%2C%20including%20the%20UN%20Charter%20and%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraelis%20and%20Palestinians%20will%20not%20end%20this%20conflict%20on%20their%20own.%20The%20history%20is%20too%20complicated%2C%20the%20politics%20too%20polarised%2C%20the%20compromises%20required%20too%20difficult.%20But%20peace%20cannot%20be%20imposed%20from%20outside.%20It%20requires%20bold%20leaders%20with%20legitimacy%20and%20credibility%20among%20their%20peoples%2C%20and%20a%20commitment%20to%20two%20states%20living%20together%20peacefully.%20Those%20leaders%20are%20not%20currently%20in%20power%20in%20Palestine%20or%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20USA%20cannot%20bring%20peace%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20on%20its%20own.%20You%20can%20help%20build%20a%20new%20coalition%20for%20peace%2C%20including%20countries%20from%20the%20region%20and%20Europe%20who%20want%20a%20just%20settlement.%20This%20coalition%20can%20restore%20a%20political%20horizon%2C%20and%20rebuild%20the%20trust%20needed%20for%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProgress%20will%20not%20be%20easy%2C%20or%20quick.%20Years%20of%20mistrust%20and%20violence%20have%20left%20the%20two%20peoples%20far%20from%20readiness%20to%20negotiate.%20A%20comprehensive%20agreement%20will%20take%20years.%20It%20will%20demand%20enormous%20political%20courage%20from%20all%20leaders%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20significant%20domestic%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20is%20the%20time%20to%20start.%20A%20serious%20peace%20plan%20is%20not%20a%20distraction%20from%20resolving%20the%20current%20crisis%3B%20it%20is%20a%20prerequisite.%20There%20is%20a%20slender%20opportunity%20to%20build%20on%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20UN%20Security%20Council%20Resolution.%20But%20progress%20is%20more%20likely%20if%20that%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20a%20lasting%20peace%2C%20not%20just%20de-escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDe-escalation%20is%20not%20enough.%20We%20cannot%20go%20back%20to%20managing%20the%20conflict.%20It%20will%20erupt%20again%20and%20again%20with%20more%20death%20and%20misery.%20The%20conflict%20must%20be%20resolved%2C%20permanently%2C%20through%20negotiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%2C%20you%20said%20last%20month%20that%20American%20leadership%20is%20what%20holds%20the%20world%20together.%20This%20conflict%20is%20tearing%20the%20world%20apart.%20We%20have%20spoken%20to%20Israelis%20whose%20families%20were%20murdered%20and%20taken%20hostage%2C%20and%20Gazans%20suffering%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe.%20We%20recognise%20their%20pain%2C%20anger%20and%20fear.%20We%20encourage%20you%20and%20Secretary%20Blinken%20to%20continue%20working%20to%20release%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20and%20end%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Elders%20learned%20from%20our%20founder%2C%20Nelson%20Mandela%2C%20that%20the%20road%20from%20hatred%20to%20forgiveness%20can%20be%20long%20and%20difficult.%20Some%20will%20never%20walk%20it.%20But%20the%20majority%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20Israelis%20want%20to%20live%20in%20peace%2C%20not%20endure%20yet%20more%20violence.%20Please%20help%20them%20find%20the%20path%20to%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20will%20never%20forget%20your%20leadership%20if%20you%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESigned%20by%20the%20Elders.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700194289000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17093901%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-9.38.00.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-elders-joe-biden-israel-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Members%20of%20the%20organisation%20founded%20by%20Nelson%20Mandela%20told%20Biden%20that%20the%20US%20can%20help%20build%20a%20new%20coalition%20for%20peace%2C%20including%20countries%20from%20the%20region%20and%20Europe%20who%20want%20a%20just%20settlement%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-elders-joe-biden-israel-palestine%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Luis%20Diaz's%20father%20weeps%20as%20his%20son%20scores%20twice%20for%20Colombia%20against%20Brazil%20days%20after%20release%20by%20kidnappers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700193360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F70x70%2Fskynews-luiz-diaz-luis-manuel-diaz_6363159.jpg%3F20231117035916%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fluis-diazs-father-weeps-as-his-son-scores-twice-for-colombia-against-brazil-days-after-release-by-kidnappers-13009982%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Luis%20Diaz's%20father%20was%20in%20tears%20on%20Thursday%20after%20he%20watched%20his%20son%20score%20both%20goals%20for%20Colombia%20in%20a%202-1%20win%20over%20Brazil%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%20qualifying%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A632%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fluis-diazs-father-weeps-as-his-son-scores-twice-for-colombia-against-brazil-days-after-release-by-kidnappers-13009982%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fluis-diazs-father-weeps-as-his-son-scores-twice-for-colombia-against-brazil-days-after-release-by-kidnappers-13009982%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fluis-diazs-father-weeps-as-his-son-scores-twice-for-colombia-against-brazil-days-after-release-by-kidnappers-13009982%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20People%20Killed%20By%20Aerial%20Bombing%20Don't%20Matter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17091305%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-9.12.38%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20November%2017%2C%2041%20days%20into%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20continuous%20bombardment%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F16%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fuk-labour-party-ceasefire-vote-gaza.html%5C%22%3EUK%20Parliament%20voted%20against%20a%20motion%20calling%20for%20an%20ceasefire%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bombing%20continues%2C%20and%20one%20question%20stands%20out%3A%20Why%201%2C200%20people%20killed%20by%20guerillas%20matter%20more%20to%20Western%20governments%20than%2012%2C000%20%E2%80%93%20and%20counting%20%E2%80%93%20killed%20by%20bombs%20from%20the%20sky.%20Why%20one%20is%20a%20barbaric%20crime%2C%20and%20the%20other%20a%20civilised%20military%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20correct%20answers%20to%20that.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20the%20history%20of%20bombing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20single%20line%3A%20From%20its%20beginnings%2C%20over%20a%20hundred%20years%20ago%2C%20aerial%20bombing%20was%20a%20technology%20meant%20for%20colonial%20powers%20to%20use%20exclusively%20against%20colonised%2C%20usually%20indigenous%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20hundred%20years%2C%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20monopoly%20over%20that%20most%20lethal%20violence%20has%20conditioned%20how%20we%20see%20the%20victims%20of%20bombs%20%E2%80%93%20if%20we%20see%20them%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20aeroplanes%20to%20drop%20lethal%20explosives%20is%20nearly%20as%20old%20as%20powered%20flight%20itself.%20The%20technology%20was%20primitive%20when%20the%20First%20World%20War%20broke%20out%20in%20Europe%2C%20and%20never%20became%20a%20decisive%20military%20factor%20in%20the%20war.%20Afterwards%2C%20though%2C%20its%20potential%20was%20obvious%3A%20the%20danger%20and%20the%20power%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESven%20Lindqvist%2C%20in%20his%20inventive%20book-essay%20%3Cem%3EA%20History%20of%20Bombing%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20describes%20what%20followed%20in%20the%20inter-war%20years.%20European%20governments%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Prepared%20treaties%20to%20never%20bomb%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Decided%20to%20use%20colonial%20targets%20as%20sites%20to%20test%2C%20refine%20and%20advance%20the%20technology%20of%20bombing%20from%20the%20air%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Began%20creating%20air%20forces%20primarily%20for%20%E2%80%98aerial%20policing%E2%80%99%3A%20which%20often%20meant%20bombing%20tribal%20villages%20prone%20to%20political%20unrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritain%2C%20to%20take%20one%20example%2C%20was%20a%20victorious%20nation%20in%201919%2C%20but%20cash-strapped%20and%20shaken%2C%20with%20its%20hold%20on%20empire%20slipping.%20One%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20named%20Winston%20Churchill%2C%20came%20to%20hold%20three%20portfolios%20at%20the%20same%20time%3A%20for%20The%20Colonies%2C%20Air%20and%20War.%20With%20Hugh%20Trenchard%2C%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20first%20chief%20of%20air%20staff%2C%20Churchill%20conceived%20a%20military%20doctrine%20%E2%80%93%20also%20a%20budgetary%20argument%20%E2%80%93%20for%20%E2%80%9Caerial%20policing%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20far%20reaches%20of%20the%20empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20power%2C%20they%20realised%2C%20could%20relieve%20the%20empire%20of%20costly%20army%20garrisons.%20As%20young%20men%20and%20soldiers%2C%20both%20Churchill%20and%20Trenchard%20had%20served%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpolicing%E2%80%9D%20of%20colonial%20frontiers%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20in%20Waziristan%20and%20West%20Africa%20respectively.%20Churchill%E2%80%99s%20first%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EWith%20the%20Malakand%20Field%20Force%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20described%20the%20arduous%20work%20of%20exacting%20collective%20punishment%20on%20Pashtuns.%20Regiments%20advanced%2C%20dynamiting%20buildings%2C%20felling%20orchards%20and%20filling%20up%20wells%20with%20rocks%20and%20gravel%20(tactics%20still%20favoured%20by%20Israeli%20settlers%20and%20the%20IDF%20against%20Palestinian%20villages%20in%20the%20West%20Bank).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternatively%2C%20Churchill%20wrote%2C%20they%20%E2%80%9Cdestroyed%20all%20the%20villages%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20valley%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20valley%20was%20filled%20with%20the%20smoke%2C%20which%20curled%20upwards%20in%20dense%20and%20numerous%20columns%2C%20and%20hung%20like%20a%20cloud%20over%20the%20scene%20of%20destruction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comparative%20efficiency%20of%20achieving%20this%20from%20the%20air%2C%20with%20bombing%20raids%2C%20was%20obvious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fguernica3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-139765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22556%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPablo%20Picasso%E2%80%99s%20Guernica.%20Photo%3A%20pablopicasso.org%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201920%2C%20the%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20carried%20out%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20first%20systematic%20bombing%20campaign%20against%20Somalis.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20first%20societies%20in%20to%20experience%20bombing%20were%20in%20Iraq%2C%20North%20and%20East%20Africa%2C%20and%20the%20North-West%20Frontier%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArthur%20Harris%2C%20later%20a%20legend%20of%20British%20bomber%20command%2C%20said%20this%20early%20in%20his%20career%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Arab%20and%20Kurd%20now%20know%20what%20real%20bombing%20means%2C%20in%20casualties%20and%20damage.%20They%20know%20that%20within%2045%20minutes%2C%20a%20full-sized%20village%20can%20be%20practically%20wiped%20out%2C%20and%20a%20third%20of%20its%20inhabitants%20killed%20or%20injured.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20an%20eerie%20continuity%20between%20those%20places%20and%20the%20ones%20still%20being%20bombed%20on%20Western%20order%20a%20century%20later.%20While%20writing%20my%20own%20book%20%3Cem%3EFarthest%20Field%3A%20An%20Indian%20Story%20of%20the%20Second%20World%20War%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%202013%2C%20I%20researched%20the%20bombing%20raids%20on%20two%20Pashtun%20villages%2C%20Ahmed%20Khel%20and%20Datta%20Khel%2C%20in%201941.%20Looking%20up%20their%20names%20online%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20those%20exact%20villages%20were%20still%20being%20punished%20by%20Predator%20drones%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Western%20ethics%20of%20aerial%20bombing%2C%20wrote%20Sven%20Lindqvist%2C%20made%20this%20very%20clear%3A%20%E2%80%98The%20laws%20of%20war%20protect%20enemies%20of%20the%20same%20race%2C%20class%2C%20and%20culture.%20The%20laws%20of%20war%20leave%20the%20foreign%20and%20the%20alien%20without%20protection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201940s%2C%20once%20World%20War%20II%20broke%20out%20in%20Europe%2C%20these%20rules%20could%20not%20hold.%20And%20there%20was%20hell%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bombing%20of%20Guernica%20in%201937%2C%20by%20German%20and%20Italian%20air%20forces%2C%20was%20a%20herald%20that%20civilian%20bombardment%20would%20be%20turned%20against%20Europeans%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20always%20happens%2C%20and%20is%20the%20central%20insight%20of%20Lindqvist%E2%80%99s%20writings%3A%20technologies%20of%20control%20meant%20for%20colonial%20peripheries%20come%20home%20to%20roost%20in%20the%20metropole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20years%20of%20World%20War%20II%20were%20an%20exception.%20In%20the%20post-war%20world%2C%20bombing%20resumed%20on%20the%20same%20racial%2C%20colonial%20lines%20and%20geographies%2C%20right%20through%20the%20US%20wars%20on%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%20in%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20two%20countries%20push%20this%20colonial%20perversity%20into%20newer%20and%20deadlier%20expressions%3A%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Israel.%20Since%20October%2C%20reports%20say%20Israel%20has%20dropped%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20explosives%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20That%20is%20equivalent%20to%20two%20nuclear%20bombs.%20The%20Gaza%20Strip%20has%20an%20area%20about%20one%20quarter%20the%20size%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20deflection%20and%20defence%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20%E2%80%93%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20trying%20to%20hit%20civilians%2C%20Hamas%20is%20at%20fault%20for%20placing%20its%20fighters%20among%20civilians%20%E2%80%93%20is%20old%20news%2C%20straight%20from%20a%20hundred-year-old%20textbook%20for%20colonial%20collective%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20Israeli%20commanders%20have%20been%20saying%20it%20out%20loud%2C%20from%20day%20one%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20emphasis%20is%20on%20damage%2C%20not%20on%20accuracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20hundred%20years%2C%20our%20moral%20imagination%20of%20war%20has%20been%20shaped%20by%20colonizing%20states%20which%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20bomb%20from%20the%20air%2C%20and%20want%20to%20use%20it%3A%20Against%20tribes%20on%20their%20own%20native%20land.%20Against%20people%20with%20barely%20any%20defences.%20Against%20civilians.%20The%20perpetrators%20of%20this%20mass%20killing%20are%20always%20coded%20as%20civilized.%20The%20victims%20are%20always%20at%20best%20invisible%2C%20at%20worst%20sub-human.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20also%20been%20conditioned%20is%20our%20visual%20imagination.%20For%20weeks%2C%20most%20images%20from%20Gaza%20only%20showed%20explosions%20from%20a%20distance%2C%20collapsing%20buildings%2C%20smoking%20ruins.%20When%20we%20do%20see%20the%20victims%20%E2%80%93%20children%20buried%20alive%20under%20masonry%2C%20or%20people%20carrying%20the%20destroyed%20bodies%20of%20their%20friends%2C%20looking%20for%20help%20%E2%80%93%20we%E2%80%99re%20trained%20to%20not%20see%20them%20as%20fully%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2026%2C%20weeks%20into%20the%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%2C%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20voted%20overwhelmingly%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%2C%20durable%20and%20sustained%20humanitarian%20truce%E2%80%9D.%20One%20hundred%20and%20twenty%20countries%20votes%20in%20favour%20and%2014%20voted%20against.%20India%20was%20among%20the%2045%20that%20abstained.%20It%20was%20a%20measure%20of%20the%20real%20international%20demand%20for%20Israel%20to%20stop%20bombing.%20But%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20double%20standards%20have%20been%20unmoving%2C%20with%20hugely%20damaging%20effects%20on%20what%20survives%20of%20international%20law%20and%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20you%20read%20this%2C%20more%20people%20in%20Gaza%20are%20being%20buried%20alive%20by%20bombs%2C%20and%20Western%20leaders%20will%20not%20utter%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98ceasefire%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20for%20that%3A%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20a%20few%20years%20in%20the%201940s%2C%20the%20people%20being%20bombed%20from%20the%20air%20were%20rarely%20European.%20And%20except%20for%20one%20day%20in%202001%2C%20they%20were%20never%20American.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20people%20dropping%20the%20bombs%20usually%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERaghu%20Karnad%20is%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Dorothy%20and%20Lewis%20B.%20Cullman%20Center%20for%20Scholars%20%26amp%3B%20Writers%2C%20New%20York%20Public%20Library%2C%202022-23.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700192689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17091305%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-9.12.38%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fisrael-gaza-palestine-aerial-bombing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20West%E2%80%99s%20monopoly%20over%20this%20most%20lethal%20violence%20has%20conditioned%20how%20we%20see%20the%20victims%20of%20bombs%20%E2%80%93%20if%20we%20see%20them%20at%20all.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fisrael-gaza-palestine-aerial-bombing%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20Tijara%2C%20Rajasthan's%20'Yogi'%20Talks%20of%20Rising%20Above%20Caste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085333%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-8.51.43.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ETijara%20(Rajasthan)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20small%20DJ%20truck%20followed%20by%20a%20series%20of%20SUVs%20winds%20its%20way%20along%20narrow%20tracks%2C%20throwing%20up%20clouds%20of%20dust%20as%20it%20approaches%20a%20village.%20A%20few%20children%20run%20towards%20the%20convoy%2C%20others%20climb%20on%20to%20their%20rooftops%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lyrics%20blare%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20mein%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EYogi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ne%20keeya%20kamaal%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EUP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20kee%20tarah%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ko%20bhee%20chamak%20banayenge%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EBaba%20Balaknath%20Yogi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20jinka%20chunav%20nishan%2C