fter%20the%20Mev%20Muslims.%20In%20a%20close%20contest%20in%202018%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20Sanjeev%20Yadav%20defeated%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Aimaduudin%20Durru%20Mian%20with%20a%20thin%20margin%20of%203%25.%20Which%20is%20why%2C%20Balaknath%20is%20ensuring%20that%20his%20campaign%20takes%20him%20to%20as%20many%20Dalit%20villages%20he%20can%20go%20to%20on%20any%20given%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085213%2FCrowd-watching-Tapookra-JPG-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085213%2FCrowd-watching-Tapookra-JPG-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085213%2FCrowd-watching-Tapookra-JPG-1-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085213%2FCrowd-watching-Tapookra-JPG-1-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685133%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECrowd%20watching%20Tapookra.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Nimahedi%20village%2C%20as%20a%20group%20of%20women%20begin%20to%20complain%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20drinking%20water%2C%20Balaknath%E2%80%99s%20men%20nudge%20them%20to%20touch%20his%20feet%20and%20seek%20the%20%E2%80%9CBaba%E2%80%99s%20blessings.%E2%80%9D%20In%20his%20speech%20Balaknath%20asks%20them%20to%20%E2%80%9Crise%20above%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejaati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bcaste%5D%20help%20protect%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esanatan%20dharm%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20something%20he%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20in%20his%20own%20campaign.%20Over%20the%20past%2030%20years%20the%20BJP%20has%20managed%20the%20paradoxical%20feat%20of%20appealing%20to%20an%20overarching%20Hindu%20identity%20while%20catering%20to%20the%20fragmentary%20demand%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejaati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20politics.%20This%20remains%20true%20of%20the%20Balakanth%20campaign%20who%20has%2C%20in%20part%2C%20been%20picked%20to%20contest%20from%20Tijara%20because%20he%20is%20a%20Yadav%2C%20who%20form%20the%20third%20largest%20community%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20time%20Balaknath%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20convoy%20travels%20past%20the%20Yadav%20villages%2C%20the%20songs%20blaring%20from%20the%20DJ%20truck%20change.%20The%20lyrics%20now%20emphasise%20the%20caste%20identity%20of%20Balaknath%E2%80%99s%20family%20%E2%80%93%20his%20mother%20Urmila%20Devi%20and%20father%20Subhash%20Yadav.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20music%20makes%20me%20recall%20what%20Shahun%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Mewati%20Yuva%20Sangathan%2C%20had%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20Y%20%2B%20M%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20here%20it%20becomes%20Y%20versus%20M.%20Yadavs%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%20speak%20of%20Samajwad%2C%20here%20they%20target%20Muslim.%E2%80%9D%20The%20constituency%20has%20seen%20the%20battle%20between%20the%20Mevs%20and%20the%20Yadavs%20play%20ever%20since%20Independence%2C%20with%20the%20Mevs%20winning%20seven%20out%20of%2012%20assembly%20elections%2C%20and%20the%20Yadavs%20the%20other%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAssured%20of%20Yadav%20backing%2C%20Balaknath%20knows%20the%20Dalits%20hold%20his%20electoral%20fate%20in%20their%20hand.%20We%20continue%20following%20the%20Balaknath%20convoy.%20At%20Bhamraka%20village%2C%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20addressing%20villagers%2C%20he%20evokes%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20but%20makes%20sure%20he%20refers%20to%20Babasahab%20Ambedkar%20as%20well%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20only%20other%20law%20minister%20from%20your%20community%20that%20the%20country%20has%20seen%20is%20Arjun%20Singh%20Meghwal.%20The%20BJP%20gave%20him%20this%20position%2C%20it%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20decision.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20repeats%20this%20in%20village%20after%20village%2C%20ending%20his%20speeches%20with%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-jai-shri-ram-as-a-political-slogan-is-a-cover-for-violence%5C%22%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Ratan%20Baba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar%20Amar%20Rahe%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prominence%20given%20to%20Arjun%20Singh%20Meghwal%20in%20Rajasthan%20campaign%20ties%20in%20directly%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20Meghwals%20make%20up%20around%2025%20%25%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Dalit%20population%20and%20have%20growing%20sense%20of%20their%20assertion%20as%20a%20community.%20While%20much%20of%20Meghwal%20politics%20plays%20out%20in%20western%20Rajasthan%2C%20Jodhpur%20and%20Marwar%2C%20here%20in%20Tijara%2C%20the%20Meghwals%20form%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20Dalit%20electorate%20and%20here%2C%20this%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20appeal%C2%A0%20to%20the%20larger%20Dalit%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17084425%2FF_DBNXRbcAAoIye.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17084425%2FF_DBNXRbcAAoIye.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17084425%2FF_DBNXRbcAAoIye-300x157.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17084425%2FF_DBNXRbcAAoIye-1024x536.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685132%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EArjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40arjunrammeghwal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20entrance%20of%20Mirchuki%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ewe%20speak%20to%20some%20of%20the%20Dalit%20families%20soon%20after%20Balaknath%E2%80%99s%20convoy%20leaves.%20Ram%20Rati%20says%20she%20will%20vote%20for%20%E2%80%9CModi%E2%80%9D.%20When%20I%20ask%20her%20why%2C%20she%20says%20it%E2%80%99s%20because%20he%20has%20given%20them%20mobile%20phones.%20Her%20son%2C%20Deshraj%2C%20a%20daily%20wage%20carpenter%2C%20corrects%20her%20brusquely%2C%20telling%20her%20the%20phones%20came%20from%20Gehlot%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20says%20people%20here%20will%20vote%20according%20to%20their%20preferences%2C%20but%20most%20will%20choose%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESitting%20in%20their%20family%20home%2C%20Deshraj%E2%80%99s%20father%20Daya%20Chand%20and%20his%20two%20brothers%20bear%20out%20his%20words.%C2%A0%20They%20favour%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20are%20unimpressed%20with%20Balaknath%20and%20his%20team.%20They%20admit%20that%20%E2%80%9CHindu-Hindu%E2%80%9D%20is%20working%20in%20a%20section%20of%20their%20community%2C%20but%20feel%20that%20even%20though%20he%20is%20working%20hard%2C%20his%20campaign%20is%20losing%20traction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20show%20us%20a%20video%20they%20have%20just%20received%20on%20their%20mobile%20phones%2C%20showing%20Sikhs%20in%20a%20neighbouring%20village%20shout%20anti-Balaknath%20slogans%20during%20his%20election%20sabha.%20The%20Sikhs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fanti-minority-stand-sgpc-bjp-leader-hate-speech-sandeep-dayma%5C%22%3Eremain%20angry%20at%20Sandeep%20Dayama%2C%20a%20prominent%20BJP%20Gujjar%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fbjp-gurdwaras-comment-rajasthan-assembly-polls-9012323%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehate%20speech%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20large%20number%20of%20gurdwaras%20have%20come%20up%20recently%20in%20Tijara%E2%80%A6so%20it%20is%20our%20religious%20responsibility%20to%20uproot%20these%20open%20sores%20from%20here.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDayama%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20the%20party%20and%20later%20retracted%20his%20statement%20and%20apologised%20with%20a%20clarification%20which%20was%20as%20hateful%20%E2%80%93%20he%20said%20he%20meant%20%E2%80%9Cmasjids%20and%20mazhars%2C%E2%80%9D%20not%20gurdwaras.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDaya%20Chand%20and%20his%20brothers%20also%20speak%20of%20a%20new%20factor%20that%20is%20generating%20interest.%20Udmiram%2C%20a%20Gujjar%20sarpanch%20has%20joined%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%E2%80%99s%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20or%20ASPA%2C%20which%20is%20in%20a%20coalition%20with%20Hanuman%20Beniwal%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party.%20In%20a%20cluster%20of%20Gujjar%20homes%20in%20Milakpur%2C%20people%20speak%20with%20some%20excitement%20at%20the%20prospects%20of%20a%20man%20from%20their%20community%20challenging%20the%20Yadav%20domination%20of%20the%20region.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20about%20Mahant%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20vote%20for%20Baba%20Balaknath%20to%20prove%20we%20are%20Hindus.%20If%20his%20supporters%20talk%20about%20him%20being%20a%20Yadav%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20support%20our%20Gujjar%20%3Cem%3Eneta%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085953%2FMirchuki-village-tijara-IMG_582.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085953%2FMirchuki-village-tijara-IMG_582.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085953%2FMirchuki-village-tijara-IMG_582-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085953%2FMirchuki-village-tijara-IMG_582-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685136%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMirchuki%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%20Tijara%2C%20Alwar%20District.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20meet%20Bane%20Singh%20of%20the%20BJP%20at%20Chandrlok%20City%2C%20a%20hotel%20complex%20in%20Tijara%20town%2C%20he%20dismisses%20Udhami%20as%20inconsequential%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20bring%20him%20into%20the%20fold%2C%20we%20will%20get%20Purshottom%20Saini%20released%20from%20jail%20so%20all%20the%20Sainis%20will%20vote%20for%20us.%20Sandeep%20Dayama%20will%20return%20to%20campaign%20for%20Baba%20and%20even%20Congress%20leaders%20like%20Deshpal%20will%20join%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAiming%20to%20impress%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20busy%20man%20but%20agreed%20to%20meet%20you%20as%20I%20want%20every%20sister%20of%20mine%20to%20know%20the%20truth%20of%20this%20region.%20Tijara%20will%20lead%20the%20way%20in%20making%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reference%20to%20Purshottam%20Saini%20ties%20back%20to%20a%20recent%20incident%20that%20served%20to%20magnify%20the%20politics%20of%20polarisation%20Balaknath%20represents.%20Saini%20was%20arrested%2C%20along%20with%20three%20others%20after%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fyouth-thrashed-over-remark-on-bajrang-dal-dies-in-rajasthan%2Farticleshow%2F103647440.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ekilling%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%2020-year-old%20Wakeel%20Mohammad.%20The%20Muslim%20youth%20was%20abducted%20and%20beaten%20to%20death%20after%20a%20clash%20over%20allegations%20that%20he%E2%80%99d%C2%A0%20been%20made%20about%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal.%20Saini%20is%20a%20local%20advocate%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20other%20Hindutva%20groups%20have%20attacked%20Gehlot%20for%20appeasing%20Muslim%20sentiments%20by%20wrongly%20jailing%20him.%20Bane%20Singh%20says%20the%20Saini%20community%20are%20upset%20and%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20get%20Purshottam%20released%20shortly%20before%20the%20elections.%20When%20asked%20how%20they%20will%20do%20this%2C%20he%20smiles%2C%20shaking%20his%20head%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDekhtey%20raho%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bkeep%20watching%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20if%20on%20cue%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20he%20had%20referred%20to%2C%20Deshpal%20arrives%20at%20the%20hotel.%20Over%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20he%20tells%20us%20how%20the%20Congress%20banished%20him%20when%20he%20protested%20against%20the%20candidature%20of%20Imran%20Khan.%20A%20newspaper%20carried%20an%20article%20with%20the%20headline%20that%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20leaders%20were%20exiting%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%20Deshpal%20says%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20his%20quote%20but%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20ask%20why%20the%20Congress%20gives%20tickets%20only%20to%20Mevs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20flirtation%20with%20men%20like%20Deshpal%20is%20a%20good%20indication%20of%20how%20close%20this%20fight%20is%20turning%20out%20to%20be.%20Both%20Adityanath%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20are%20due%20to%20address%20rallies%20in%20the%20constituency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17090227%2FIMG_5918-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17090227%2FIMG_5918-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17090227%2FIMG_5918-1-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17090227%2FIMG_5918-1-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685137%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBalaknath%20speaks%20at%20a%20campaign%20event.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShahun%20says%20many%20in%20the%20Mev%20community%20are%20heartened%20by%20the%20very%20fact%20that%20a%20headline-grabbing%2C%20BJP%20mahant%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20biggest%20BJP%20leaders%20is%20having%20to%20fight%20hard%20to%20win%20Tijara.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImran%20Ayyub%2C%20who%20works%20in%20Bhidwadi%2C%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMewat%20has%20seen%20so%20much%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20lynchings%2C%20hate%20speeches%20and%20hate%20crimes%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20still%20anxious%20about%20what%20lies%20ahead%20if%20Balaknath%20wins.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20From%20his%20one-room%20office%2C%20he%20points%20to%20the%20view%20outside%2C%20a%20thick%20cover%20of%20smog%20that%20hangs%20low%20over%20a%20pot-holed%20road%2C%20%E2%80%9CBhiwadi%20is%20part%20of%20the%20NCR%20region%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20the%20neglected%20step-children%20of%20that%20area.%20Here%2C%20we%20just%20get%20to%20hear%20about%20thee%20great%20work%20the%20Congress%20has%20done%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDevelopment%20issues%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20are%20forced%20to%20take%20backseat%20for%20him%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20as%20Muslims%20it%20is%20about%20life%20and%20liberty%20above%20all%20for%20them.%20It%20is%20only%20a%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20that%20has%20ensured%20the%20polarisation%20does%20not%20reach%20the%20level%20witnessed%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20Mewat%20lying%20across%20the%20border%20in%20Haryana.%20Balaknath%20as%20an%20MP%20under%20a%20Congress%20government%20is%20better%20than%20Balaknath%20as%20an%20MLA%20in%20a%20BJP%20government%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20what%20happened%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20Kala%20Pahad.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKala%20Pahad%20is%20a%20ridge%20of%20the%20Aravallis%20which%20separates%20Rajasthan%20from%20Haryana%20dividing%20Mewat%20in%20two.%20He%20does%20not%20have%20to%20spell%20out%20how%20the%20Mevs%20have%20fared%20in%20Haryana%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700192101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085333%2FScreenshot-2023-11-17-at-8.51.43.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahant-baba-balaknath-rajasthan-election-yogi-adityanath%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alwar%20MP%20Balaknath's%20comparison%20with%20Adityanath%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%2C%20is%20deliberately%20and%20ubiquitously%20evoked%20by%20BJP%20on%20stickers%2C%20posters%20and%20billboards%20across%20the%20constituency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahant-baba-balaknath-rajasthan-election-yogi-adityanath%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wayne's%20World%20star's%20son%20dies