0very%20well%20to%20the%20Igloos.%20Of%20course%2C%20they%20had%20a%20few%20doubts%2C%20and%20some%20would%20ask%20me%20if%20it%20would%20fall.%20I%20would%20sometimes%20explain%20to%20them%20the%20construction%20process%20to%20assure%20them%20that%20they%20are%20safe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20process%20of%20making%20an%20Igloo%2C%20Vinod%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20terms%20of%20time%2C%20construction%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Igloo%2C%20it%20all%20depends%20on%20the%20ice.%20The%20snow%20that%20falls%20in%20December%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334115%2Fbest-homestays-in-himachal-pradesh-uttarakhand-to-enjoy-snowfall-in-winter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowder%20snow%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it%20does%20not%20stick%20easily.%20We%20have%20to%20water%20it%20to%20make%20it%20stick%20and%20it%20takes%20longer%20for%20us%20to%20make%20the%20Igloo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20snow%20in%20the%20later%20days%20is%20thicker%20and%20more%20stable%2C%20it%20only%20takes%20a%20day%20to%20complete%20the%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20shape%20of%20the%20Igloo%20is%20oval%20because%20it%20distributes%20the%20weight%20into%20equal%20parts.%20As%20the%20temperature%20drops%2C%20the%20ice%20crystals%20begin%20to%20cement.%20Eventually%2C%20they%20become%20so%20crystallised%20that%20the%20structure%20becomes%20rock%20solid%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCoy2n5JpDMl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCoy2n5JpDMl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_bl