20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325308%2Frare-wildlife-conservation-photos-from-across-the-world-nature-infocus-kalyan-varma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20photographers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20brave%20deep%20forests%2C%20remote%20areas%20and%20harsh%20terrain%2C%20are%20to%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20year%2C%20it%20was%20Bengaluru-native%20Vihaan%20Talya%20Vikas%E2%80%99s%20photography%20that%20grabbed%20eyeballs.%20The%2010-year-old%E2%80%99s%20winning%20shot%20is%20telling%20in%20and%20of%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ornamental%20tree%20trunk%20spider%20preventing%20its%20prey%20from%20escaping%2C%20with%20a%20carving%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%20in%20the%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVihaan%E2%80%99s%20shot%20bagged%20the%20prize%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9810%20years%20and%20under%E2%80%98%20category.%20This%20came%20as%20a%20pleasant%20surprise%20to%20the%20Class%205%20student%20of%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Kumaran%20School.%20%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20it%20was%20anticipated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20recalling%20the%20unassuming%20day%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333532%2Fpadma-shri-t-s-satyan-father-of-indian-photojournalism-mysuru-bengaluru-history-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclicked%20the%20picture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20visiting%20a%20tamarind%20grove%20at%20Nalluru%20along%20with%20my%20dad%20and%20his%20friends.%20We%20stopped%20by%20the%20Gopalaswamy%20Temple%20to%20admire%20the%20carvings%20of%20Lord%20Krishna.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20spotted%20the%20spider%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVihaan%E2%80%99s%20first%20thought%20was%2C%20how%20well-positioned%20the%20arachnid%20was.%20It%20almost%20seemed%20entranced%20by%20Lord%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20flute.%20Insects%2C%20particularly%20spiders%2C%20had%20always%20held%20a%20fanc