fer%20employment%20once%20we%20completed%20our%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20her%20enthusiasm%20was%20curbed%20by%20the%20people%20around%20her.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20neighbours%20and%20our%20family%20friends%20were%20against%20sending%20the%20women%20of%20the%20house%20outside%20to%20work.%20They%20doubted%20our%20ability%20to%20earn%20anything%2C%20but%20my%20mother-in-law%20stood%20up%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20both%20Namita%20and%20her%20sister-in-law%20had%20also%20assumed%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255089%2Fdr-m-aishwarya-coimbatore-parenting-network-tamil-nadu-taboo-how-to-donate-breast-milk-feeding-awareness-taboo-myths-banks-postpartum-depression-covid-19-pandemic-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20role%20of%20mothers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20had%20additional%20responsibilities.%20%E2%80%9COur%20husbands%20and%20my%20mother-in-law%20decided%20to%20show%20faith%20in%20us%20and%20gave%20us%20immense%20support%20to%20go%20for%20the%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother-in-law%20would%20take%20care%20of%20our%20kids%20when%20we%20attended%20the%20training%20sessions.%20She%20would%20also%20help%20us%20in%20household%20work%20and%20ensure%20we%20had%20enough%20time%20to%20perfect%20our%20craft%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20was%20being%20held%20by%20an%20NGO%20called%20%E2%80%98Keshav%20Srushti%E2%80%99%20headed%20by%20Gaurav%20Shrivastava.%20It%20was%20an%20initiative%20to%20promote%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%20and%20make%20them%20financially%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20initiative%2C%20Gaurav%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initiative%20began%20to%20empower%20tribal%20women%20financially%20in%20the%20region.%20Despite%20abundant%20bamboo%20production%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20utilised%20effectively.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20organised%20self-help%20groups%20to%20train%20women%20in%20creating%20bamboo%20products%2C%20which%20would%20then%20be%20sold%20nationwide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Namita%20has%20trained%20over%2057%20women%20from%20around%20her%20village%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-5-1700058095-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENamita%20has%20trained%20over%2057%20women%20from%20around%20her%20village.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Namita%20Namdev%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20informs%20that%20this%20Diwali%2C%20they%20sold%20more%20than%203%2C000%20bamboo%20%3Cem%3Ekandils%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9COur%20products%20are%20not%20only%20sold%20in%20India%20but%20throughout%20the%20world.%20We%20now%20have%2023%20villages%20and%20700%20women%20making%20bamboo%20products%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20products%2C%20Gaurav%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initiative%E2%80%99s%20main%20goal%20was%20always%20to%20give%20alternative%20livelihood%20to%20tribal%20women%2C%20but%20we%20also%20wanted%20to%20bring%20alternative%20eco-friendly%20products%20into%20the%20market.%20All%20our%20products%20are%20natural%20and%20made%20100%20percent%20out%20of%20bamboo.%20We%20want%20to%20spread%20the%20message%20of%20sustainability%20too%20with%20our%20initiative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20bring%20the%20second%20income%20in%20my%20home%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20period%20was%20about%2030%20days%20long%2C%20says%20Namita.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Gaurav%20sir%20asked%20us%20what%20are%20the%20uses%20of%20bamboo%2C%20I%20was%20not%20sure%20how%20to%20answer%20his%20question.%20We%20would%20sometimes%20use%20it%20to%20make%20carriers%20but%20that%20was%20it.%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20how%20many%20useful%20things%20can%20be%20made%20from%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20training%20period%20was%20over%2C%20we%20started%20to%20get%20some%20work.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20used%20to%20get%20fewer%20orders%2C%20but%20we%20kept%20working%20hard.%20Soon%2C%20we%20received%20more%20orders.%20I%20had%20faith%20that%20if%20we%20kept%20on%20working%2C%20the%20demand%20would%20increase%20and%20we%20would%20make%20more%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTogether%2C%20we%20have%20now%20established%20a%20company%20by%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Vikramgad%20Bamboo%20Udyog%20Producer%20Company%20Limited%E2%80%99%20and%20we%20will%20soon%20be%20taking%20orders%20online%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20Namita%20now%20makes%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%209%2C000%20every%20month.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20very%20proud%20that%20I%20am%20able%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20household%20income.%20I%20finish%20my%20household%20work%2C%20then%20help%20my%20husband%20with%20the%20field%20work%20before%20proceeding%20to%20work%20on%20the%20bamboo%20pieces%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20adding%20that%20the%20work%20gives%20them%20the%20flexibility%20to%20take%20it%20up%20whenever%20they%20have%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-6-1700058322.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20group%20makes%20products%20such%20as%20kandils%20(sky%20lanterns)%2C%20phone%20holders%2C%20rakhis%2C%20dustbins%2C%20and%20much%20more.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-6-1700058322.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-6-1700058322-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-6-1700058322-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-6-1700058322-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnow-6-1700058322-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20group%20makes%20products%20such%20as%20kandils%20(sky%20lanterns)%2C%20phone%20holders%2C%20rakhis%2C%20dustbins%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Namita%20Namdev%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamita%20has%20also%20trained%20multiple%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F65802%2Fpalak-gaur-cleanliness-village-kanpur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20women%20in%20her%20village%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20nearby%20villages%20in%20the%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20as%20many%20women%20to%20be%20independent%20as%20possible.%20I%20have%20trained%20more%20than%2057%20women%20so%20far%20and%20hope%20to%20train%20more.%20With%20the%20establishment%20of%20our%20company%2C%20we%20are%20hoping%20to%20get%20