.%20Srikanth%20got%20back%20the%20encroached%2025-acre%20land%2C%20cleaned%20it%20and%20planted%207%2C000%20trees%20in%20the%20area.%20He%20spent%20more%20than%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20collector%20gave%20me%2025%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20workers%20to%20help%20me%20with%20the%20work.%20In%20a%20year%2C%20the%20forest%20grew%20well%20and%20became%20home%20to%20many%20birds%20and%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srikanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHe%20planted%20native%20trees%20and%20fruits%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20like%20jamun%2C%20peepal%2C%20fig%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201040px)%20100vw%2C%201040px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Srikanth%20invested%20Rs%201.5%20lakhs%20to%20build%20the%20forest%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426.jpeg%201040w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-13-at-18.12.11-1699969426-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334105%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESrikanth%20invested%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20to%20build%20the%20forest.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20social%20forest%2C%20built%20on%20the%20riverbed%2C%20can%20help%20prevent%20soil%20erosion%2C%20according%20to%20environmental%20scientist%20Praveen%20Kumar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20is%2C%20say%20100%20acres%20of%20land%20under%20paddy%20cultivation%2C%20people%20would%20build%20a%20small%20forest%20in%20between%2C%20to%20help%20cross%20pollination.%20The%20birds%20and%20snakes%20in%20the%20forest%20would%20keep%20rats%20and%20insects%20away%20from%20the%20crops.%20The%20forest%20that%20Srikanth%20has%20created%20will%20prevent%20soil%20erosion.%20It%20has%20also%20become%20a%20hub%20for%20birds%2C%20with%20over%2055%20species%20habiting%20the%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Praveen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20says%20that%20had%20Srikanth%20not%20taken%20the%20efforts%20to%20create%20this%20forest%2C%20it%20would%20have%20become%20a%C2%A0sand%20quarry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20success%20of%20this%20forest%2C%20Srikanth%20has%20created%20a%20Miyawaki%20forest%20in%20a%201-acre%20land%20and%20another%20forest%20in%20Pernambut.%20He%20has%20also%20planted%20fruit%20trees%20in%20villages%20across%20Vellore%2C%20which%20would%20help%20villagers%20get%20an%20income%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332769%2Fgeorge-remedios-plants-food-forests-trees-in-mumbai-limited-spaces-rooftop-gardens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20forests%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20wastelands%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20all%20busy%20earning%20assets%20for%20our%20next%20generation.%20I%20believe%20that%20increasing%20the%20green%20cover%20and%20building%20such%20forests%20is%20the%20biggest%20asset%20we%20can%20leave%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srikanth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699970361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMy-work-view-16-1699969285.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Braving%20threats%20from%20the%20real%20estate%20mafia%2C%20G%20Srikanth%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20singlehandedly%20grew%20a%20forest%20on%20a%2025-acre%20land%20near%20the%20Palar%20river.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suicidal%20After%20Failing%20to%20Crack%20IIT-JEE%2C%20Engineer%20Helps%20Over%2010%2C000%20Students%20Find%20Hope%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20suicide%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngineer%20Tharun%20Sai%E2%80%99s%20Hyderabad-based%20platform%20%E2%80%98FindHope%E2%80%99%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20ever%20experienced%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332931%2Fnamarita-kathait-started-the-listening-circles-promote-mental-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloneliness%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feeling%20he%20battled%20for%20most%20of%20his%20life.%20It%20was%20a%20series%20of%20events%20that%20led%20to%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20mental%20health%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gruelling%20preparation%20for%20the%20IIT-JEE%20exam%20coupled%20with%20the%20stress%20and%20isolation%20the%20pandemic%20brought%20with%20itself%20were%20among%20the%20few%20events.%20But%20the%20real%20jolt%20came%20when%20he%20watched%20some%20of%20his%20own%20college%20mates%20die%20by%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFindHope%20helps%20youth%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2024%20by%20connecting%20them%20with%20peers%20pursuing%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20psychology%